[SN]TITLE[SN]
Road closed for burst main repairs in Flintshire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A road in Flintshire will remain closed overnight as work continues to repair a burst water main.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The A5119 in the New Brighton area of Mold has been closed in both directions and traffic has been reported to be heavy during Monday.
A team from Welsh Water is on site repairing the main.
The company has apologised for the inconvenience and said some customers may notice discolouration of their tap water when the supply is restored.
